      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON GYPSY (5) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from four starts. Placed last time (29.73) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 6 lengths. Has the ability and should feature. FLYING ARTIE (8) hit the ground running off an inside draw last start and was never headed (19.24) at Angle Park in a Grade 5 over 342m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Leading chance again. SHIMA MOON (4) jumped from box 5 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.38. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Likely to be in the finish. COMPTON FRANKY (1) is in the mix after placing last time out.",
